<div class=\"site_frame\"> \n      <section> \n       <div id=\"bk5019\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_init cssskin-_block_billboard\" data-bk-id=\"bk5019\"> \n        <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n         <div class=\" c-body\"> \n          <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n           <picture> \n            <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6397/information_banner_20190526095941163.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n            <img src=\"../_src/6397/information_banner_20190526095941163.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6397_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n           </picture> \n          </div> \n         </div> \n        </div> \n       </div> \n       <div id=\"bk5020\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-h2_midashi2\" data-bk-id=\"bk5020\"> \n        <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"top\"> \n         <h4 class=\" c-small_headline\">&nbsp; <span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;新着情報</span></h4> \n        </div> \n       </div> \n      </section> \n     </div> \n    </div> \n    <main> \n     <div id=\"a-site_contents\" class=\"a-site_contents  noskin\"> \n      <article> \n       <div class=\"site_frame\"> \n        <div class=\"g-column\"> \n         <div id=\"a-main\" class=\"a-main column -col8 \"> \n          <section> \n           <div id=\"bk5028\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5028\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"221125\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">青森営業所 事務所棟開設</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.11.25&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5029\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5029\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <p class=\" c-body\">この度、青森営業所の敷地内に新事務所棟を建設し、11月14日より新建屋にて営業をスタート致しました<br>今後もお客様のニーズに合わせた商品やサービスを提供できるよう精進して参りますので、変わらぬお引き立ての程宜しくお願い致します<br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">青森営業所</span><br><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">〒039-3212 </span><br><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#434343;\">青森県上北郡六ヶ所村尾駮字野附216番地2　</span><br><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#434343;\">TEL 0175-71-1355　FAX 0175-72-2883</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body\">\n                &nbsp; \n               <br> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6406/aomori_1000.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6406/aomori_1000.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6406_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5030\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5030\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"221123\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\">冬季休業のご案内</span></span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> 2022.11.23 \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               平素は格別のご高配を賜り、厚く御礼を申し上げます \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               &nbsp; \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               誠に勝手ながら&nbsp; \n              <span style=\"color:#1c4587;\"><span class=\" d-bold\">2022年12月29日(木)〜2023年1月4日(水) </span></span>の期間を \n              <span style=\"color:#1c4587;\"><span class=\" d-bold\">冬季休業</span></span>とさせて頂きます \n             </div> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span class=\" d-bold\"><span style=\"color:#a61c00;\">2023年1月5日(水)より通常通り営業</span></span>致します<br>&nbsp;<br>お客様にはご不便をお掛けいたしますが、ご理解とご協力のほど宜しくお願い致します</p> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5031\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5031\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220905\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">ツールdeフェスタ2022 開催終了致しました</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.9.5&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5032\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5032\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">新型コロナウイルスの感染拡大により3年越しの開催が実現した展示即売会</span><br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">第13回ツールdeフェスタ2022のキャッチコピーは</span><br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">「この夏 リアル再始動」　</span><br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">会場は開催両日500名を超える多くのご来場者をお迎えし、</span><br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">大変賑わいのある催しとなり終了いたしました</span><br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">たくさんのご来場を頂き誠にありがとうございました</span><br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"color:#000000;\">ツールdeフェスタ2022事務局</span></p> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5033\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5033\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6409/dsc04445_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1000,height=668\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6408/dsc04445_1.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6408/dsc04445_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6408_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6411/dsc04360_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1000,height=668\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6410/dsc04360_1.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6410/dsc04360_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6410_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5034\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5034\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6413/dsc04444_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1000,height=668\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6412/dsc04444_1.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6412/dsc04444_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6412_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6415/dsc04392_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1000,height=668\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6414/dsc04392_1.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6414/dsc04392_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6414_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5035\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5035\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220811\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">青森営業所 事務所棟建設中！</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.8.11&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5036\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_narrow c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5036\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">青森営業所では、最新のオフィス環境と</span> \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">セキュリティー機能を備えた<br>事務所棟の建設工事を進めています<br>竣工は、本年１０月末竣工予定です</span> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6417/aomori.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1477,height=1108\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6416/aomori.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6416/aomori.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1477\" height=\"1108\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6416_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5037\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5037\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220807\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">熱いぞ熊谷！2022</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.8.7&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5038\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_narrow c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5038\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">皆様ご承知の通り今年も「熱いぞ熊谷！」です!!</span> \n               <br> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">所員一同何とか乗り切ろうと思います…。</span> \n               <br> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">皆様も体調管理にはくれぐれもお気を付けください。</span> \n               <br> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\"></span> \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">熊谷営業所 スタッフ一同</span> \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n               <span style=\"color:#000000;\">#サマータイム要希望！</span> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6419/img_4936_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=3000,height=4000\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6418/img_4936_1.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6418/img_4936_1.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"3000\" height=\"4000\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6418_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5039\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5039\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220711\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\">夏季休業のご案内</span></span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> 2022.07.11 \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               平素は格別のご高配を賜り、厚く御礼を申し上げます \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               &nbsp; \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               誠に勝手ながら&nbsp; \n              <span style=\"color:#1c4587;\"><span class=\" d-bold\">2022年8月13日(土)〜8月16日(火)</span></span>の期間を \n              <span style=\"color:#1c4587;\"><span class=\" d-bold\">夏季休業</span></span>とさせて頂きます \n             </div> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span class=\" d-bold\"><span style=\"color:#a61c00;\">8月17日(水)より通常通り営業</span></span>致します<br>&nbsp;<br>お客様にはご不便をお掛けいたしますが、ご理解とご協力のほど宜しくお願い致します</p> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5040\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5040\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220516\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">レンタル新商品のご案内</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.5.16&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5041\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_narrow c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5041\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                新規レンタル品として右記アイテムを導入しました \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                詳細・ご不明点は弊社営業担当までお問い合わせください \n              </div> \n              <p class=\" c-body\">&nbsp;</p> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"https://www.sankotech.co.jp/new_item/03208_denyo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6420/03208.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6420/03208.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"793\" height=\"1122\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6420_1\" class=\" c-no_adjust\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5042\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5042\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220419\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">ウクライナ支援を行いました</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\"></span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022. 4. 19</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5043\" class=\"b-both_diff -right_large -sp-single_column c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5043\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column\"> \n             <div class=\" column -col7 -col_main\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                大変な状況となっているウクライナへの支援としてユニセフに寄付を行い、感謝状を頂きました \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -col5 -col_sub\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6423/img20220420221418824436.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=1653,height=2338\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6422/img20220420221418824436.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6422/img20220420221418824436.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"1653\" height=\"2338\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6422_1\" class=\" c-no_adjust\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5044\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5044\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220412\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">ちばSDGsパートナー企業に登録されました</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\"></span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022. 4. 12</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5045\" class=\"b-both_diff -right_large -sp-single_column c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5045\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column\"> \n             <div class=\" column -col7 -col_main\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                「ちばSDGsパートナー登録制度」とは、県内企業等におけるSDGs推進の機運を醸成するとともに、具体的な取組みを後押しするため千葉県により創設された制度です \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                サンコーテック株式会社は持続可能な社会の実現に向けて積極的に取り組んで参ります \n              </div> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n                &nbsp; \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -col5 -col_sub\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <a href=\"../_src/6425/img20220421093853954983.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=793,height=1122\"> \n                 <picture> \n                  <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6424/img20220421093853954983.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                  <img src=\"../_src/6424/img20220421093853954983.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"793\" height=\"1122\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6424_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                 </picture></a> \n               </div> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5046\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5046\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220322\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">動産補償及び基本料制度運用開始のご案内とお願い</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> 2022.03.22&nbsp; \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5047\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5047\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n             <div class=\" c-body\"> \n              <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n               <picture> \n                <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6428/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                <img src=\"../_src/6428/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.png?v=1767099951882\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6428_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n               </picture> \n              </div>補償制度の詳細につきましては \n              <a href=\"https://www.sankotech.co.jp/Information/pdf/動産補償制度のご案内.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">こちらのPDFよりご確認ください</a> \n              <br>&nbsp; \n              <br> \n              <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n               <a href=\"https://www.sankotech.co.jp/Information/pdf/20220322.pdf\" class=\"js-popup\" data-width=\"1000\" data-height=\"600\" data-resize=\"true\"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6426/img20220323192900691622.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6426/img20220323192900691622.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"595\" height=\"841\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6426_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture></a> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5048\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5048\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220315\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">レンタル新商品のご案内</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\" data-sitecolor-text=\"\">2022.3.15&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               新規レンタル品として下記2アイテムを導入しました \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               詳細・ご不明点は弊社営業担当までお問い合わせください \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               &nbsp; \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5049\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_narrow c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5049\"> \n            <div class=\" g-column -col2 -sp-col1\"> \n             <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6434/00406_denyo.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6434/00406_denyo.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"793\" height=\"1122\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6434_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture> \n               </div> \n               <br> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6430/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6430/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.png?v=1767099951882\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6430_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture> \n               </div> PDFは \n               <a href=\"https://www.sankotech.co.jp/new_item/00406_denyo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">こちらから</a> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" column -column2 -column-lasts\"> \n              <div class=\" c-body\"> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6436/01110_hataya.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6436/01110_hataya.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"793\" height=\"1122\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6436_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture> \n               </div> \n               <br> \n               <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6432/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6432/file_type_pdf_icon_130274.png?v=1767099951882\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6432_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture> \n               </div> PDFは \n               <a href=\"https://www.sankotech.co.jp/new_item/01110_hataya.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">こちらから</a> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5050\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk5050\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"220314\"> \n             <p class=\" c-body\"><span style=\"color:#073763;\" class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-bold\">新型コロナウイルス感染者発生に関するお知らせ</span></span></p> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <hr class=\"c-hr\"> 2022.03.14&nbsp; \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk5051\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-padding_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main -js-bindZoom\" data-bk-id=\"bk5051\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n              <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n               <a href=\"../_src/6439/img20220313101925652784.jpg?v=1767099951882\" class=\"js-zoomImage\" rel=\"width=595,height=841\"> \n                <picture> \n                 <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6438/img20220313101925652784.webp?v=1767099951882\"> \n                 <img src=\"../_src/6438/img20220313101925652784.jpg?v=1767099951882\" width=\"595\" height=\"841\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc6438_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n                </picture></a> \n              </div> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\